PREAMBLE

This license is designed to protect the open-source community by ensuring that
major corporations cannot take this framework and monetize it without giving back
to the community that created it. The goal is to keep AI research accessible and
collaborative while preventing exploitation by large commercial entities.

If you are part of the open-source community and wish to monetize this framework,
you are encouraged to contact the author to discuss collaboration and licensing
opportunities that benefit both parties and the broader community.

